column1: # The vertical profiles in this file were derived from a simulation with the
# hemispheric version of CMAQv5.2.1 for the year 2016 and represent the annual
# average values at the model grid cell closest to lat 37N
# they are reflective of conditions in a remote marine environment.
# Grid spacing: 108 x 108 km on a polar stereographic grid covering the northern hemisphere
# The vertical sigma levels used in the simulations were 1.0
# The hourly meteorological and air quality fields used to derive these profiles
